# Sales Performance Dashboard

## Project Overview

This project is an interactive Power BI dashboard created to analyze sales performance and business KPIs.

## Tools Used

* Power BI
* Excel
* DAX

## Dashboard Features

* Total Sales Analysis
* KPI Cards
* Monthly Trends
* Regional Performance
* Interactive Filters

## Insights

* Identified sales growth trends
* Compared regional performance
* Visualized business metrics

